nodes.text: Moro Y'Arano was a male Genian who was Talesan Fry's Executive in charge of business outreach at Fry Industries. At the time of the Clone Wars, Y'Arano was completely sealed off from the outside world in 20 BBY. He took part in a meeting with a group led by the Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi, who had come to negotiate with the Fry Industries about the code breaker.
